How Great Thou Art

COVID-19 Statement
Fountainview Academy is a boarding high school in British Columbia, Canada.  Our entire school – students and staff families – all live on the campus and are a single learning group under the BC Ministry of Education’s COVID-19 requirements.  The “audience” at this concert is made up of staff families who are part of the learning group with the students involved.


Get exclusive access to exciting content and our entire DVD library all while helping to support us at https://patreon.com/fountainview

If you enjoyed this video, don’t forget to subscribe and enable notifications for our channel so you never miss an upload!

Students from all over the world are attracted to Fountainview because of its balanced approach to education.
